WHERE "w"."DefinitionId" IN (
    SELECT "f"."value"
    FROM json_each(@__filter_DefinitionIds_0) AS "f"
) AND "w"."IsPublished"
ORDER BY "w"."Name"

    LIMIT @__p_4 OFFSET @__p_3
) AS "t"
ORDER BY "t"."Sequence"
